{"word":"τωθάζω","slug":"τωθάζω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>τωθάζω</b></el> <p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>to mock, scoff</i> or <i>jeer at, flout</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b>: —<a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a> <i>to be jeered</i>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><a href='S:absolute, absolutely'>absol.</a> <i>to jeer</i>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}